headline: Omnicom Group (OMC) Stock Trades Up, Here Is Why
summary: Shares of global advertising giant Omnicom Group (NYSE:OMC) jumped 3.9% in the afternoon session after BNP Paribas Exane adjusted its price target on the company to $120 from $115.
